Firstly I plugged all the wires in their respective ports

i plugged in console cables in all the switches and routers and connected them to the pc for configuration


I checked the device manager for the port number of the console of the switch of the Newyork router and Switch they were shown as COM12 and COM15

I opened Putty app and selected the port and entered the configuration of the switch and router in two different putty sessions respectively.

I entered the Network Configuration setting in each of the PC's to assign ip addresses to them.

upon clicking the ipv4 address adapter setting in each of them,

